-- UBI Banca revises accords with British insurer Aviva
-- By Lisa Jucca
-- Wed Apr 16, 2014 02:51AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, April 16 (Reuters) - Italy's UBI Banca <UBI.MI> has agreed to sell Aviva <AV.L> a further 30 percent stake in two life bancassurance ventures, previously jointly controlled, and buy back from the British insurer minority stakes in three of its bank units.

